0, 703.0]]], "lines": ["何が", "結婚しよう、", "だよ！"]}, {"box": [214, 473, 307, 654], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28, "lines_coords": [[[276.0, 473.0], [307.0, 473.0], [307.0, 654.0], [276.0, 654.0]], [[243.0, 475.0], [271.0, 475.0], [273.0, 604.0], [245.0, 604.0]], [[214.0, 473.0], [240.0, 473.0], [240.0, 581.0], [214.0, 581.0]]], "lines": ["やっぱり今度も", "無理だった", "じゃん！！"]}, {"box": [934, 828, 1056, 1020], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28, "lines_coords": [[[1028.0, 828.0], [1056.0, 828.0], [1051.0, 995.0], [1023.0, 995.0]], [[998.0, 831.0], [1020.0, 831.0], [1020.0, 1004.0], [998.0, 1004.0]], [[962.0, 829.0], [989.0, 829.0], [990.0, 1020.0], [964.0, 1020.0]], [[934.0, 831.0], [956.0, 831.0], [956.0, 957.0], [934.0, 957.0]]], "lines": ["「再就職なんて", "その気になりゃ", "余裕」とか言って", "全然だし！！"]}, {"box": [584, 790, 675, 1005], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25, "lines_coords": [[[648.0, 790.0], [675.0, 790.0], [675.0, 946.0], [648.0, 946.0]], [[615.0, 792.0], [642.0, 792.0], [642.0, 968.0], [615.0, 968.0]], [[584.0, 792.0], [606.0, 792.0], [609.0, 1003.0], [587.0, 1003.0]]], "lines": ["ま．．．しばらく", "就職はキビしい", "かもしれないけど、"]}, {"box": [421, 1084, 481, 1300], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[451.0, 1084.0], [479.0, 1084.0], [481.0, 1218.0], [453.0, 1218.0]], [[421.0, 1084.0], [448.0, 1084.0], [450.0, 1300.0], [423.0, 1300.0]]], "lines": ["もういいよ、", "当てにしてないよ。"]}, {"box": [118, 881, 217, 1040], "vertical": true, "font_size": 33, "lines_coords": [[[184.0, 884.0], [217.0, 884.0], [217.0, 976.0], [184.0, 976.0]], [[154.0, 882.0], [185.0, 882.0], [185.0, 1040.0], [154.0, 1040.0]], [[118.0, 882.0], [153.0, 881.0], [156.0, 951.0], [121.0, 953.0]]], "lines": ["大丈夫、", "俺にも考えは", "ある。"]}, {"box": [698, 1264, 823, 1445], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[795.0, 1270.0], [822.0, 1270.0], [822.0, 1395.0], [795.0, 1395.0]], [[764.0, 1267.0], [790.0, 1267.0], [790.0, 1426.0], [764.0, 1426.0]], [[731.0, 1265.0], [757.0, 1265.0], [756.0, 1445.0], [729.0, 1445.0]], [[701.0,